# Stray CLI-flag-shaped files at repo root — these are always errors
# from someone running `basefwx ... --password=output.fwx` where the
# shell wrote the output to a file literally named "--password". Block
# them at root so they can't ever be committed.
/--*

# Example plugin build artifacts (already covered by `build/` but listed
# explicitly so the intent is obvious to anyone reading this file).
# 3.7.0 added: aead-wrapped-keyed/, time-tweak/, static-embed/ — all
# match the wildcard.
examples/plugins/*/build/
examples/plugins/*/bin/

# Leak-detect helpers (3.7.0+): the C++ ASan probe writes into
# build-asan-leak/ (matched by build-*/ above); the Java heap probe
# writes into .leak-java/ when run locally outside the CI workflow.
.leak-java/
